278
00:11:26.129 --> 00:11:27.672
<i>Dad! Dad. no!</i>

279
00:11:27.696 --> 00:11:29.369
<i>Please! Dad. I love you!</i>

280
00:11:29.393 --> 00:11:31.299
<i>- Help! Please!
- [STATIC DRONES]</i>

281
