295
00:12:00.206 --> 00:12:01.227
- I called.
- OK.

296
00:12:01.251 --> 00:12:03.055
I was at a basketball game.

297
00:12:03.079 --> 00:12:04.317
This kid of mine has got me
schlepping around the city

298
00:12:04.341 --> 00:12:05.535
